{
  "stem": "1363.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I know that we sometimes when nobody was watching, we took out from the earth, carrots, and ate it raw as it was.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So it gave us a bit of vitamins and whatever.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So eventually when we arrived in Gonyu, and my auntie wasn't there, I started and tried to take my trip back.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now funny enough, on that station they announced it that anyone who can prove that they are either sick or they can't walk anymore or they are between 16 and 60 again-- or they, who are under 16 and over 60, they should come to that part of standing on the side.",
      "word_count": 52
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the other was the normal 16 to 60 should be here.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then they take them out over the border, most probably to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I never knew where they went to, because I haven't met any of them coming back.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that was the time when I tried to take off.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So what I've done, I said I am under 16.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was a German soldier, SS, standing-- it was a big yard, with a well in the middle, where the well had a bucket to pull out some water from it.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the SS was standing on the side, I remember without a hat.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I remember it was already October.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was like October, end of October, beginning of November.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he was standing there in a very casual way, with his riding boots still here.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I'll never forget his face.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And as we were lining up, and he was trying to do a Mengele-- you to the right, you to the left.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I said, I am under 16.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He said, you're not 16.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You're over 17, which I was.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I looked older.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I had a scarf on my head.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
